      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "REAPER (2) had some strong recent form but was below best last time when fifth (25.84) in a Mix 3/4 at Warrnambool. Spotted a start off the low draw last time. The form out of last race has been strong. Worth another chance. GRAB THE GOLD (1) has a strong record this trip with three wins and two placings from nine starts. Was out of placings last time (26.14) at Warragul in a Grade 4, finishing fifth and beaten 5.5 lengths. Can hit the frame with the right run. FURIOUS FALCON (5) stalked lead from an outside box last start before finishing second (29.11) at this track in a Grade 4/5 over 510m. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to be in the finish again. VALVE BOUNCE (3) was a winner two back then strongly fancied last time but could only manage a third (24.83) at this track.",
